collection.name: Shiba Social Club Official Collection
collection.description:
The Shiba Social Club is an Elite club for the baddest of the Shiba. Our NFT collection has 7,777 unique hand-drawn Shiba with the best detail in the industry.

Our members gain access to our metaverse game and land in the Sandbox. We have hosted many holders only poker games with one totaling over $20k in prize money. And those are just a few of the perks you get by being an Elite member of The Shiba Social club. In the Shiba Social Club everyone is treated like a VIP.
